<h3 class="h4 m3">Video playlists about Choice</h3>
<div class='row row-skinny row-sm-2up'>
<div class='col'>
<div class='m2'>
<h4 class='h7 m3'>What makes you happy?</h4>
<div class='row row-skinny row-oh-2up'>
<div class='col'>
<a href='/playlists/4/what_makes_you_happy'>
<span class="thumb thumb--square"><span class="thumb__sizer"><span class="thumb__tugger"><img alt="" class=" thumb__image" play="false" src="https://tedcdnpi-a.akamaihd.net/r/tedcdnpf-a.akamaihd.net/images/playlists/what_makes_you_happy.jpg?quality=89&amp;w=256" /><span class="thumb__aligner"></span></span></span></span>
</a>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='meta m4'>
13 talks
&bull;
<span class='meta__val'>3h 20m</span>
</div>
<div class='p4'>Everyone wants to be happy. But how, exactly, does one go about it?  Here, psychologists, journalists, Buddhist monks and more gives answers that may surprise.</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='m2'>
<h4 class='h7 m3'>Our brains: predictably irrational</h4>
<div class='row row-skinny row-oh-2up'>
<div class='col'>
<a href='/playlists/74/our_brains_predictably_irrati'>
<span class="thumb thumb--square"><span class="thumb__sizer"><span class="thumb__tugger"><img alt="" class=" thumb__image" play="false" src="https://tedcdnpi-a.akamaihd.net/r/tedcdnpf-a.akamaihd.net/images/playlists/our_brains_predictably_irrational.jpg?quality=89&amp;w=256" /><span class="thumb__aligner"></span></span></span></span>
</a>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='meta m4'>
12 talks
&bull;
<span class='meta__val'>3h 19m</span>
</div>
<div class='p4'>The 3 pounds of jelly in our skulls allow us to reflect on our own consciousness -- and to make counterintuitive, irrational decisions. These talks explore why.</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='m2'>
<h4 class='h7 m3'>Everything you thought ... was wrong</h4>
<div class='row row-skinny row-oh-2up'>
<div class='col'>
<a href='/playlists/91/everything_you_thought_was'>
<span class="thumb thumb--square"><span class="thumb__sizer"><span class="thumb__tugger"><img alt="" class=" thumb__image" play="false" src="https://tedcdnpi-a.akamaihd.net/r/tedcdnpf-a.akamaihd.net/images/playlists/everything_you_thought_was_wrong.jpg?quality=89&amp;w=256" /><span class="thumb__aligner"></span></span></span></span>
</a>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='meta m4'>
10 talks
&bull;
<span class='meta__val'>2h 43m</span>
</div>
<div class='p4'>10 counterintuitive talks to flip your thinking on everything from shoes to aid organizations to the universe.</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
